`.editorconfig`: indentation for `package.json`

`.editorconfig`: indentation for `package.json`

The indent size used in the `package.json` file cannot be changed,
it will always be 2 spaces. See https://github.com/npm/npm/pull/3180#issuecomment-16336516

Remove outdated JSHint options

Since JSHint v2.5 the `trailing` and `smarttabs` JSHint options
are removed.

Ref https://github.com/jshint/jshint/releases/tag/2.5.0
